about.description:
spaCy is a library for advanced natural language processing in Python and
Cython.

name: spacy
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "spacy" %}
{% set version = "3.1.1" %}
{% set sha256sum = "77a0f78d7e65335e5fae13af7e55684770c76a0457ee1baac414ddb89b5df6e4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256sum }}
  patches: patches/0001-remove-bad-grc-test-file.patch


build:
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cython                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - numpy                                  # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - numpy
    - setuptools
    - wheel
    - cython >=0.25,<3.0
    - murmurhash >=0.28.0,<1.1.0
    - cymem >=2.0.2,<2.1.0
    - preshed >=3.0.2,<3.1.0
    - thinc >=8.0.8,<8.1.0
    - cython-blis >=0.4.0,<0.8.0
  run:
    - python
    # Our libraries
    - spacy-legacy >=3.0.7,<3.1.0
    - murmurhash >=0.28.0,<1.1.0
    - cymem >=2.0.2,<2.1.0
    - preshed >=3.0.2,<3.1.0
    - thinc >=8.0.8,<8.1.0
    - cython-blis >=0.4.0,<0.8.0
    - wasabi >=0.8.1,<1.1.0
    - srsly >=2.4.1,<3.0.0
    - catalogue >=2.0.4,<2.1.0
    # Exclude typer with unpinned click
    - typer >=0.3.2,<0.4.0
    - pathy >=0.3.5
    # Third-party dependencies
    - tqdm >=4.38.0,<5.0.0
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - requests >=2.13.0,<3.0.0
    - pydantic >=1.7.4,!=1.8,!=1.8.1,<1.9.0
    - jinja2
    # Official Python utilities
    - setuptools
    - packaging >=20.0
    - typing_extensions >=3.7.4,<4.0.0.0  # [py<=37]

test:
  requires:
    - pytest
    - pytest-timeout
    - mock
    - hypothesis
    - importlib-metadata ==3.3.0  # [py<38]
  imports:
    - spacy
  commands:
    - python -m pytest --tb=native --pyargs {{ name }}

about:
  home: https://spacy.io/
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Industrial-strength Natural Language Processing
  description: |
    spaCy is a library for advanced natural language processing in Python and
    Cython.
  doc_url: https://spacy.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/explosion/spaCy

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rmax
    - honnibal
    - ines
    - adrianeboyd
